videoSnippet.title: What a Fighter Yuliya Shvayger is! She Set a Nice Trap and Ekaterina Walked Straight Into it.
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator The Krystyna Hołuj–Radzikowska Women's Grandmaster Chess Tournament is a 10-player round-robin taking place from 28 November to 6 December 2017 in Hotel HP Park Plaza in Wrocław, Poland. Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, with a 30-second increment from move one. No draw offers are allowed before move 30.

Shvayger, Yuliya (ISR) - Atalik, Ekaterina (TUR)
Radzikowska WGM Tournament 2017 round 02
